PrecisSetting apart of some 15.38 hectares of land situated on Vancouver Island, in the Rupert District of British Columbia, for the use and benefit of the NUWITTI BAND OF INDIANS (also known as the Tlatlasikwala Band) as an addition to Hope Island Indian Reserve No. 1.
